translation.Name: Belgium Note - Cave Afzetters #1
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_0: Supply run to Ridders Van Licht HQ:
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: A couple guys will pose as refugees and gain access of the HQ from the inside.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_4: A few more guys will distract the guards at the gate, while the men inside will hijack the helicopter.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_6: Once the situation is under control we will flee back to the cave. Assemble our men and ultimately flee Belgium.
